description: A very cold day in Prague. No more sunny days on the beach, I guess. Don´t worry though, I´ll try to bring you more outdoor action in the future. But today I got seduced by a nice flat just few meters away. Well, not by the flat itself but by it´s owner, a 23 years old bricklayer named Radek. I met him when he was on the way from the gym. I was a little afraid he might be too tired to even talk. I know such a feeling. But he was okay and quite willing to chat. I fed him some modeling job nonsense and he was all mine, listening to my every word. Maybe it was a bit overkill move on my part, the boy really needed cash and it was easy to convince him to do some nasties. 30 minutes and two climaxes later I was totally broke and sucked dry. A better result than I hoped for :-)
title: Czech Hunter 271
